<div id="pf60" class="pf w5 h13" data-page-no="60"><div class="pc pc60 w5 h13"><div class="t m1c3 x21 hb ybcc ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">96 </div><div class="t m5cf x4 h34 ybcd ff1 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Every member: </div><div class="t m249 x80 h34 ybce ff1 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">praying . . giving . </div><div class="t m24b x70 ha y2bf ff3 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">proclaim the resurrection with such confidence, power, and effective-</div><div class="t m35d x70 ha y2c0 ff3 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ness! If they had known the story to be a lie, why would so many of </div><div class="t m123 x70 ha ya3b ff3 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">them have been willing to lay down their lives for their faith? </div><div class="t m326 x21 hb ybcf ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">13. Why can we witness for Christ with confidence and courage, </div><div class="t m2af x30 hb y442 ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">whatever our circumstances? Matt. 28:18, 20; compare Acts 4:31. </div><div class="t m314 x21 hb y4c1 ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">AM I REJOICING IN CHRIST&apos;S DEATH AND RESURRECTION? </div><div class="t m12a x70 ha ybd0 ff3 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">• </div><div class="t m3ae x75 ha ybd0 ff3 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What has happened in my life as I have accepted the truth of </div><div class="t md5 x70 ha ybd1 ff3 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Christ&apos;s death and resurrection? </div><div class="t m12a x20 ha ya6a ff3 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">• </div><div class="t m452 x10 ha ya6a ff3 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Am I eager to share my knowledge of Christ with others? What </div><div class="t m54 x70 ha ybd2 ff3 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">positive experiences have I had as I have shared my faith in His death </div><div class="t m2b4 x70 ha ya6b ff3 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and resurrection? </div><div class="t m46 x21 hb ybd3 ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">FURTHER STUDY AND MEDITATION: </div><div class="t m2ab x5 ha ybd3 ff3 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Read &quot;In Pilate&apos;s Judgment </div><div class="t m601 x21 ha yb42 ff3 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Hall,&quot; &quot; &apos;It Is Finished,&apos; &quot; &quot; &apos;The Lord Is Risen,&apos; &quot; and &quot;Go Teach All </div><div class="t m38e x21 ha ybd4 ff3 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Nations,&quot; chapters 77, 79, 81, and 86 in </div><div class="t m28f x1c ha ybd4 ff6 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Desire of Ages, </div><div class="t m320 xe3 ha ybd4 ff3 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pp. 723-740, </div><div class="t mb9 x21 ha ya6d ff3 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">758-768, 779-787, and 818-828. </div><div class="t m11a x21 hb ya6f ff1 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SUMMARY: </div><div class="t m50f x31 ha ya6f ff3 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The mistreatment, death, and resurrection of Christ reveal as </div><div class="t m51c x21 ha ybd5 ff3 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">nothing else can how much God cares for sinners. No earthly king would </div><div class="t m30a x21 ha ya71 ff3 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ever act as Jesus did while possessing the power to break the bonds of </div><div class="t m43b x21 ha ybd6 ff3 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">death. When Jesus died Satan&apos;s kingdom was defeated. The penalty for the </div><div class="t m178 x21 ha ybd7 ff3 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sins of humanity was paid, and our redemption was assured. Jesus rose as </div><div class="t m27a x21 ha y9c0 ff3 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">recognized King of the universe and returned to heaven to apply for us the </div><div class="t m357 x21 ha ybd8 ff3 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">blessings of His sacrifice. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
